<div style="font-family: sans-serif; color: #1c1917;">
  <h2 style="color: #4f46e5;">Thank you for your purchase!</h2>
  <p>Hello <%= @user.name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>
  <p>Your order <strong> <%= @order.id %></strong> has been processed successfully.</p>
  
  <p>We have attached your PDF receipt to this email for your records.</p>
  
  <div style="margin: 25px 0; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e7e5e4; border-radius: 12px;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Order Summary</h3>
    <p>Total Paid: <strong>Rs. <%= number_with_precision(@order.total_price, precision: 2) %></strong></p>
    <p>Status: <%= @order.status.capitalize %></p>
  </div>

  <p>You can also view your full order history in your <%= link_to 'customer profile', user_url(@user) %>.</p>
  
  <p>Happy Reading,<br>The EBookStore Team</p>
</div>